The constructor of the only page in this wizard was: 

    public NewJtestProjectWizardPage () { 
        super ("id"); //$NON-NLS-1$ 
    } 

This throws a null pointer exception under 3.1 M6 

When we changed it to 

    public NewJtestProjectWizardPage () { 
        super ("id"); //$NON-NLS-1$ 
	setImageDescriptor(someImageDescriptor); 
    } 

the null pointer exception went away.
